column5:
Mungkin mereka potokopi nya di Snappy

*oooppssyyyy

Hey. You know what? You are loved and it’s not your fault. She was overwhelmed and she couldn’t even think about anything. So it wasn’t her fault either. You’ve been there for her, you were her only friend that made her stay alive. So you have to promise me that you will stay alive for HER *hugs*
How about tepung “Segitiga Biru” Bogasari tho?
Mending. Kalo gue ditanya “kapan nikah?” Kms.
